description:
Big sunny 1 bedroom apartment in the heart of Fort Greene. Half a block from the park and surrounded by amazing restaurants and shopping. 
"The King of all NY Blocks" ~ Time Out Magazine

Important to note: Apt. is on the 5th floor in a brownstone walk-up!

Extremely close to the C, G lines as well as walking distance to Atlantic Ave. Barclays Shopping Center 2/3,4/5, B/D, N/Q/R.

"Fort Greene is a beloved Brooklyn neighborhood that's diverse and accessible. Beyond the lush greenery of Fort Greene Park, you'll find bustling flea markets, Renowned cultural institutions and a thriving entertainment scene - all anchored by a refreshingly tight-knit community."

Extremely close to the G and C lines as well as walking distance to Atlantic Ave. Barclays Shopping Center 2/3,4/5, B/D, N/Q/R. 3 stops to Union Square on the Q.

Street parking available as well.
